  "detailed_description": "You are the <strong>Great Ancient Knight</strong>, go <strong>undercover </strong>in <strong>the Lair of the Lizards</strong>. Get <strong>Intelligence </strong>for your <strong>Knight Brothers</strong>, return the <strong>Ancient Manuscripts</strong> to the base, take the <strong>Baikal Water</strong> and <strong>Destroy the Lizard Base</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/0b5aa7b43a5729f3f80cb6e4faffeed9.avif?t=1725325521\" width=587 height=247 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Characteristics</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325521\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Call the <strong>Great Knights</strong> to your aid - <strong>Billyslav Herringtonov</strong>, <strong>Ivan Darkholmov</strong>, <strong>the God Perun</strong><br></li><li>Collect <strong>5 Ancient Manuscripts</strong><br></li><li>Drink <strong>18 cans of Baikal Water</strong><br></li><li>You have access to <strong>4 Main</strong> and <strong>2 Bonus Locations</strong> - Destroy all <strong>Lizard Bases</strong><br></li><li> <strong>15+ Cutscenes</strong> - <strong>Main Cutscenes To All Locations</strong> & <strong>Bonus Cutscenes</strong><br></li><li><strong>15+ Species of Lizards</strong><br></li><li><strong>Five Great Knights</strong> - Choose your <strong>Hero</strong><br></li><li><strong>Ancient Slavic Spaceships</strong> assembled on the basis of <strong>technologies </strong>stolen from <strong>the Lizards</strong><br></li><li><strong>Great Atmospheric Music</strong> and<strong> Sound Effects</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/6dd2055c919b9e95660c49926fa3533a.poster.avif?t=1725325521\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/6dd2055c919b9e95660c49926fa3533a.webm?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/6dd2055c919b9e95660c49926fa3533a.mp4?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Main Locations</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325521\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Lizard Camp</strong> - there is a <strong>Lizard Camp in The Forest</strong> under the walls of <strong>the Ancient Great Capital - Hyperborea</strong><br></li><li><strong>Lake Baikal</strong> - <strong>the Great Battle</strong> took place here, but now this place is <strong>under the power of the Lizards</strong>, help the Knights <strong>to return Baikal</strong> to <strong>the Native Harbor</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Mars </strong>- <strong>Diversion </strong>to <strong>the Lizard Military Base</strong> on <strong>Mars</strong><br></li><li><strong>Nibiru </strong>- Explore <strong>the Home Planet</strong> and <strong>the Main Lizard Haven</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/52de6a2044f20324ab885517dfd791c6.poster.avif?t=1725325521\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/52de6a2044f20324ab885517dfd791c6.webm?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/52de6a2044f20324ab885517dfd791c6.mp4?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bonus Locations</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/42f09af30130250fda342551860c59cb.webp?t=1725325521\" width=596 height=10 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Saint-Petersburg</strong> - <strong>Lizards </strong>have taken <strong>over the city</strong>, walk the main streets of the city and<strong> hunt down each Lizard</strong><br></li><li><strong>New Year's Winter Forest</strong> - <strong>Celebrate the New Year </strong>by chasing away<strong> the Lizards</strong> from <strong>the Great Christmas Forest</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/0eefee70d1ced7c388fc13b02c352f5c.poster.avif?t=1725325521\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/0eefee70d1ced7c388fc13b02c352f5c.webm?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230070/extras/0eefee70d1ced7c388fc13b02c352f5c.mp4?t=1725325521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
